{"sequence":20,"timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:15:28.796632783Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-1-92c13b74","body":"src/adapters/process_backend.rs:2093-2112 claims to copy the Codex transcript, but it writes the process stdout buffer to history/transcripts/codex-<invocation_id>.jsonl. The bead requires the verbatim Codex session rollout JSONL from ~/.codex/sessions; without --json, stdout is not guaranteed to contain the tool-call transcript and can omit the forensic record this change relies on. Locate/copy the actual Codex session transcript, or otherwise prove stdout is the complete transcript, and cover that distinction in the regression test.","classification":"fix_current_bead","dedup_key":"ff73b6159351d437af95d431f84c7a8c79695df9f1f70404aefd6fc206143365","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.5-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260428213321","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":21,"timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:15:28.822711752Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-1-a3e3e8a2","body":"src/adapters/process_backend.rs:396-432 now stores a natural-language last-message for Codex execution stages, and line 507 persists that same text in the raw transcript envelope. However recover_codex_structured_payload_from_stdout at src/adapters/process_backend.rs:2131-2141 still unconditionally parses envelope.last_message or stdout as JSON. If the iterative parsed sidecar is missing, the existing raw-output recovery path in src/contexts/workflow_composition/engine.rs:6817-6845 can no longer recover a completed Codex execution iteration even though the raw output exists. Update recovery to synthesize the same ExecutionPayload for Codex execution raw envelopes, or persist a recoverable synthetic payload alongside the transcript.","classification":"fix_current_bead","dedup_key":"44f75b6b00d17e1b78a78859424454bc4f8692b6836ee0725faf22489292ee4a","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.5-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260428213321","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
